Subject: [PATCH] security(ABHI-1358,1359,1361): stop sourcing GH_TOKEN.env in
 PR scripts

Replace `source ../email-security-pipeline/GH_TOKEN.env` in close_prs.sh,
fix_drafts.sh, and close_more.sh with scripts/ensure_gh_token.sh. Harden
gh_token_env.py to ignore values containing command substitution and add
regression tests for the automation scripts.

Security: CWE-78 / command injection via malicious env file content.
